trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> maintains two <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection> objects: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> specifies parameters used for matching activity status events and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> specifies parameters used to exclude activity status events from matching.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> mantiene dos objetos <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection>: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> especifica parámetros utilizados para encontrar coincidencias con eventos de estado de actividad y <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> especifica parámetros utilizados para excluir la coincidencia de los eventos de estado de actividad.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection> to an empty list.
trans-unit.target: El constructor predeterminado inicializa <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection> en una lista vacía.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection" /> class by using a list of activity locations.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una instancia nueva de la clase <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection" /> con una lista de ubicaciones de actividad.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection> is initialized to contain the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> objects specified in `locations`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection> se inicializa para contener los objetos <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> especificados en `locations`.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="locations" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="locations" /> es una referencia nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).
